            <lemma xml:id="lem-7.106">
              <statement>
                <p>
                  <ol>
                    <li>
                      <p>
                        A sequence œÜ:A ‚Üí B, Œ∏:B ‚Üí 0 is exact if and only if œÜ is onto. 
                      </p>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                      <p>
                        A sequence œÜ:0 ‚Üí B, Œ∏:B ‚Üí C is exact if and only if Œ∏ is one-to-one. 
                      </p>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                      <p>
                        If A ‚Üí B ‚Üí C ‚Üí D ‚Üí E is an exact sequence with homomorphisms œÜ:A ‚Üí B and œà:D ‚Üí E satisfying Im œÜ = B and Ker œà = 0, then C = 0.
                      </p>
